# Direct dependencies only. requirements.txt is the fully-pinned lock
# (transitive deps included) actually installed in dev/CI/prod; after
# changing this file, reinstall into a fresh venv and regenerate it with
# `pip freeze > requirements.txt` (or use pip-tools' pip-compile).
#
# NOTE: enabling STORAGE_BACKEND=s3 additionally requires boto3 (imported
# lazily by app/media/storage.py, deliberately not installed by default).

